    "patch_code": "private int compareNodePointers(\n    NodePointer p1,\n    int depth1,\n    NodePointer p2,\n    int depth2) \n{\n     if (p1 == null || p2 == null){\n            return Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n      } \n        \n      if (depth1 > depth2) {\n          int r = compareNodePointers(p1.parent, depth1 - 1, p2, depth2 );\n           return r == 0 ? 1 : r ;\n       } else if (depth1 < depth2 ){\n          int r = compareNodePointers(p1, depth1 , p2.parent, depth2 - 1 );\n           return r == 0 ? -1 : r ;\n       }\n        \n   return p1.compareWithSameDepth(p2);\n}",
